受[[2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工|2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工]]的影响，第4季的制作被迫暂停<ref name="AUTOREF23">{{cite web | last1 = Lindelof | first1 = Damon | last2 = Cuse | first2 = Carlton | date = 2007-11-05 | archivedate = 2015-01-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150120055616/http://variety.com/2007/biz/news/lost-writers-like-putting-down-a-harry-potter-book-in-the-middle-25959/ | work = ''Variety'' | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | title = ''Lost'' Writers: "Like Putting Down a ''Harry Potter'' Book in the Middle" | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2007/biz/news/lost-writers-like-putting-down-a-harry-potter-book-in-the-middle-25959/}}</ref>，节目统筹希望能让节目暂时停播，先不要播出已经拍好的8集，直到可以继续为本季拍摄更多剧集时止<ref name="AUTOREF24">{{cite web | last = Goldman | first = Eric | date = 2007-11-07 | work = ''IGN'' | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | url = http://uk.ign.com/articles/2007/11/07/writers-strike-should-lost-air-this-season | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222061501/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/07/writers-strike-should-lost-air-this-season | title = Writers Strike: Should ''Lost'' Air This Season? | deadurl = no}}</ref>。但美国广播公司推翻了这一决定，宣布无论罢工几时完结，《结局的开始》都会在2008年1月底播出<ref name="AUTOREF25">{{cite web | last = Grossman | first = Ben | date = 2007-11-07 | archivedate = 2007-12-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071228101351/http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/CA6498735.html?industryid=47168 | url = http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/CA6498735.html?industryid=47168 | title = Strike Coverage: ABC to Air Partial Season of ''Lost'' | work = ''Broadcasting & Cable'' | accessdate = 2007-12-28 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。这也成为《迷失》剧集首次在美国东部时间周四晚9点播映<ref name="AUTOREF26">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2007-12-14 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=121407_01 | title = ABC Unveils Midseason Primetime Schedule | accessdate = 2012-04-21 | archivedate = 2012-04-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120421023255/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=121407_01}}</ref>，该时段通常由《[[实习医生格蕾|实习医生格蕾]]》占据<ref name="AUTOREF28">{{cite web | last = Martell | first = Erin | date = 2008-02-13 | url = http://www.tvsquad.com/2008/02/13/second-batch-of-lost-episodes-will-follow-greys-anatomy | title = Second Batch of ''Lost'' Episodes Will Follow ''Grey's Anatomy'' | work = ''TV Squad'' | accessdate = 2011-05-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110521150913/http://www.tvsquad.com/2008/02/13/second-batch-of-lost-episodes-will-follow-greys-anatomy/ | archivedate = 2011-05-21}}</ref>，竞争激烈，关注度也高<ref name="AUTOREF27">{{cite news |last=de Moraes |first=Lisa |date=2007-12-15 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130209013440/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/12/14/AR2007121402007.html |archivedate=2013-02-09 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/12/14/AR2007121402007.html |title=Strike That!  Sans Writers, ABC Reshuffles Time Slots for ''Lost'', ''Housewives'' |publisher=''[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]'' |accessdate=2015-09-07 }}</ref>，之前的《迷失》剧集都是在周三晚播出<ref name="AUTOREF29">{{cite web | last = Dos Santos | first = Kristin | publisher = ''E!'' | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | archivedate = 2015-09-07 | deadurl = no | date = 2007-12-14 | url = http://www.eonline.com/news/8592/lost-it-s-baaack | title = ''Lost'': It's Baaack! | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150907121026/http://www.eonline.com/news/8592/lost-it-s-baaack}}</ref>。与之前3季的开局一样，《结局的开始》原本也计划在[[檀香山|檀香山]][[威基基|威基基]]的“日落海滩”举行户外[[首演|首映式]]<ref name="AUTOREF30">{{cite web | last = Lachonis | first = Jon "DocArzt" | date = 2007-10-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121022014152/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-public-premiere-planned-t-13131.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-public-premiere-planned-t-13131.aspx | title = ''Lost'' Public Premiere Planned, Time Slot Still Up in the Air | work = ''BuddyTV'' | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | archivedate = 2012-10-22 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，这里会定期在9米宽的银幕上向公众免费放映电影<ref name="AUTOREF31">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150222191806/http://sunsetonthebeach.net/waikiki_beach_movie_schedule.php | deadurl = no | url = http://www.sunsetonthebeach.net/ | title = Waikiki Beach Movie Schedule and Events | work = ''Sunset on the Beach'' | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | archivedate = 2015-02-22}}</ref>，但这次首映同样因受编剧罢工的影响而取消<ref name="AUTOREF32">{{cite web | accessdate = 2009-01-06 | last = Kunz | first = Caryn | date = 2008-01-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090106074633/http://blogs.honoluluadvertiser.com/lostinhawaii.php/2008/01/10/lost_premiere_in_waikiki | url = http://blogs.honoluluadvertiser.com/lostinhawaii.php/2008/01/10/lost_premiere_in_waikiki | title = ''Lost'' Premiere in Waikiki | newspaper = ''The Honolulu Advertiser'' | archivedate = 2009-01-06 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。剧集在电视上首播前还插播了一段名为《迷失：过去，现在和将来》（{{lang|en|''Lost: Past, Present & Future''}}）的短片<ref name="AUTOREF33">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2008-01-14 | title = A Look Over the Past Three Seasons will Attempt to Shed Some Light on Where the Survivors of Oceanic Flight 815 are and if Rescue Truly is at Hand | accessdate = 2012-03-29 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=011408_16 | archivedate = 2012-03-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120329105012/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=011408_16 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
{{lang|en|[[BuddyTV|BuddyTV]]}}网站的唐·威廉姆斯（{{lang|en|Don Williams}}）称，《结局的开始》是这年最值得期待的新季开局<ref name="AUTOREF34">{{cite web | last = Williams | first = Don | date = 2008-01-31 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002140618/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-episode-41-the-beginning-16266.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-episode-41-the-beginning-16266.aspx | title = ''Lost'': Episode 4.1 'The Beginning of the End' Live Thoughts | work = ''BuddyTV'' | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | archivedate = 2013-10-02 }}</ref>。节目首播期间及其后的6小时内一共吸引了约1613.7万美国观众收看，[[尼尔森收视率|尼尔森收视率]]调查结果显示，本集在18至49岁年龄段观众群中取得的收视率为6.7/17，这意味着全美所有该年龄段人群里有5.9%观看节目首播，而当时有看电视的该年龄段观众群中则有15%选择收看《结局的开始》<ref name="AUTOREF35">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2008-02-05 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=020508_02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120421023306/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=020508_02 | title = Weekly Primetime Ratings | accessdate = 2012-04-21 | archivedate = 2012-04-21}}</ref>，这个成绩比《迷失》之前的16集都要好，在这周的美国电视节目中排名第8<ref name="AUTOREF36">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2008-02-05 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=020508_03 | title = Weekly Program Rankings | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131228090658/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=020508_03 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-12-28 | accessdate = 2013-12-28}}</ref>。如果包括节目播出后7天内通过预录观看的人数，则共计有1776.6万观众收看本集首播<ref name="AUTOREF37">{{cite web | last = Gorman | first = Bill | date = 2008-02-24 | archivedate = 2015-01-09 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150109234511/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/02/24/top-timeshifted-broadcast-shows-jan-28-feb-3/2722/ | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/02/24/top-timeshifted-broadcast-shows-jan-28-feb-3/2722/ | title = Top Time-Shifted Broadcast Shows, Jan 28–Feb 3 | work = ''TV by the Numbers'' | accessdate = 2015-09-07 }}</ref>。《结局的开始》在加拿大一共吸引了185.5万观众，在该周所有电视节目中排名第6<ref name="AUTOREF38">{{cite web | work = ''BBM Canada'' | date = 2008-02-05 | url = http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat01282008.pdf | accessdate = 2009-03-26 | title = Top Programs – Total Canada (English) | archivedate = 2009-03-26 | deadurl = yes | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090326063844/http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat01282008.pdf}}</ref>，比第3季除开场集《[[双城记_(迷失)|双城记]]》（{{lang|en|''A Tale of Two Cities''}}）以外任何一集的成绩都好<ref name="AUTOREF40">{{cite web | work = ''BBM Canada'' | date = 2006-10-10 | url = http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat10022006.pdf | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090326063847/http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat10022006.pdf | title = Top Programs – Total Canada (English) | accessdate = 2009-03-26 | archivedate = 2009-03-26 | format = PDF}}</ref>，并且观众人数几乎是之前绝大多数剧集的两倍<ref name="AUTOREF39">{{cite web | work = ''BBM Canada'' | date = 2007-05-27 | deadurl = yes | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090327012910/http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat05212007.pdf | archivedate = 2009-03-27 | url = http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat05212007.pdf | title = Top Programs – Total Canada (English) | accessdate = 2009-03-27}}</ref>。第4季在英国也有好的开局，有110万观众收看《结局的开始》<ref name="AUTOREF41">{{cite news | last = Holmwood | first = Leigh | title = Warm Welcome for ''Lost''<nowiki>'</nowiki>s Return | date = 2008-02-03 | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/2008/feb/04/tvratings.television1 | work = ''[[卫报|The Guardian]]'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006202512/http://www.theguardian.com/media/2008/feb/04/tvratings.television1 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | archivedate = 2014-10-06}}</ref>。本集在澳大利亚首播时只有91.2万观众收看，在当晚所有电视节目里排在第15名，《[[太阳先驱报|太阳先驱报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Sun-Herald''}}）的大卫·戴尔（{{lang|en|David Dale}}）认为这样的成绩令人失望<ref name="AUTOREF42">{{cite web | last = Dale | first = David | url = http://blogs.sunherald.com.au/whoweare/archives/2008/02/the_ratings_rac_74.html | title = The Ratings Race: The Silly Season Ends Here | work = ''The Sun-Herald'' | accessdate = 2012-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120601171055/http://blogs.sunherald.com.au/whoweare/archives/2008/02/the_ratings_rac_74.html | date = 2008-02-09 | archivedate = 2012-06-01 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

