2008年1月28日，美国多位评论家拿到《结局的开始》和《[[确认死亡|确认死亡]]》的{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}。{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}网站收集的12篇评论文章全部给出好评，平均得分87<ref name="meta" />。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》的罗伯特·比安科（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）认为本集有着完美的构思，剧情扣人心弦，强势回归的《迷失》给罢工导致的电视沙漠带来绿洲<ref name="AUTOREF43">{{cite news | last = Bianco | first = Robert | date = 2008-01-30 | archivedate = 2012-11-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102104915/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2008-01-30-lost-returns_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2008-01-30-lost-returns_N.htm | title = ''Lost'' Rescues a TV Season That's Adrift | work = ''USA Today'' | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。玛丽·麦克纳马拉（{{lang|en|Mary McNamara}}）在《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》撰文称，《结局的开始》“仿佛在人的大脑最底层不断搅起情绪的化学反应，让人时而恐惧、时而歇斯底里、时而遗憾，时而又仿佛注射了[[肾上腺素|肾上腺素]]般精神为之一振……不知接下来还会给人什么样的感受”<ref name="AUTOREF44">{{cite news | last = McNamara | first = Mary | date = 2008-01-31 | url = http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2008/Feb/01/en/hawaii802010327.html | title = ''Lost'' in the Moment | newspaper = ''Los Angeles Times'' | via = The Honolulu Advertiser | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120907212635/http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2008/Feb/01/en/hawaii802010327.html | archivedate = 2012-09-07}}</ref>。《[[纽约邮报|纽约邮报]]》的亚当·巴克曼（{{lang|en|Adam Buckman}}）给予本集4星（最高4星）的高度评价<ref name="AUTOREF45">{{cite news|last=Buckman |first=Adam |date=2008-01-31 |accessdate=2012-10-18 |url=http://www.nypost.com/p/entertainment/tv/item_k1L73N4707XzxCaUPQ77zM;jsessionid=6589F9CE46D85F14BEBF89DC7A32FA7B |title=Island Fever: Thank God, At Least ''Lost'' is Back |newspaper=''[[纽约邮报|New York Post]]'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018152935/http://www.nypost.com/p/entertainment/tv/item_k1L73N4707XzxCaUPQ77zM%3Bjsessionid%3D6589F9CE46D85F14BEBF89DC7A32FA7B |archivedate=2012-10-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]]》的莫琳·瑞恩（{{lang|en|Maureen Ryan}}）表示，自己“幸福地享受（节目的）每一分钟”，还觉得“其中没有任何缺陷”<ref name="AUTOREF46">{{cite news | last = Ryan | first = Maureen | date = 2008-01-29 | url = http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/01/lost-shockers-a.html | title = ''Lost''<nowiki>'</nowiki>s Fab Start to Season 4, and a Chat with Co-Creator Damon Lindelof | newspaper = ''[[芝加哥论坛报|Chicago Tribune]]'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150715214224/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/01/lost-shockers-a.html | archivedate = 2015-07-15 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-07}}</ref>。黛安·韦茨（{{lang|en|Diane Werts}}）在《[[新闻日报|新闻日报]]》（{{lang|en|''Newsday''}}）撰文，盛赞节目表现“精湛”，娱乐性强到疯狂的程度，她在总结中认为，“《迷失》看来已经找回自我”<ref name="AUTOREF47">{{cite news|last=Werts |first=Diane |date=2008-01-30 |url=http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/tv/ny-ettell5555593jan30,0,2205345.column |title=Review: ''Lost'' Finds Itself Again in New Season |newspaper=''Newsday'' |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430215549/http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/tv/ny-ettell5555593jan30%2C0%2C2205345.column |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2008-04-30 }}</ref>。《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》的蒂姆·古德曼（{{lang|en|Tim Goodman}}）认为，本集和《确认死亡》以快速的动作和启示，给人过山车般的刺激感受，都是很好看的电视节目<ref name="AUTOREF48">{{cite news | last = Goodman | first = Tim | date = 2008-01-30 | title = Want to Get ''Lost''?  There's Still Time as Season Starts | newspaper = ''[[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]]'' | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | archivedate = 2014-11-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129022755/http://www.sfgate.com/tv/article/WANT-TO-GET-LOST-THERE-S-STILL-TIME-AS-SEASON-3230470.php | | url = http://www.sfgate.com/tv/article/WANT-TO-GET-LOST-THERE-S-STILL-TIME-AS-SEASON-3230470.php}}</ref>。马修·吉尔伯特（{{lang|en|Matthew Gilbert}}）在《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Boston Globe''}}）上指出，“《迷失》仍然能够让人脉动加速、头皮发麻……仍然是电视上最扣人心弦的剧集”<ref name="AUTOREF49">{{cite news | last = Gilbert | first = Matthew | date = 2008-01-31 | title = ''Lost'' Finds New Ways to Intrigue | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150124043743/http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2008/01/31/lost_finds_new_ways_to_intrigue/ | work = ''The Boston Globe'' | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | archivedate = 2015-01-24 | url = http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2008/01/31/lost_finds_new_ways_to_intrigue/}}</ref>。《[[明星纪事报|明星纪事报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Star-Ledger''}}）的艾伦·塞平沃尔（{{lang|en|Alan Sepinwall}}）表示，虽然他也不知道“《迷失》中余下的这么多谜团将来是否都有会令人满意的答案……但只要接下来的剧集都像这两集这样吓人、热闹、感人而刺激，那就都无所谓了”<ref name="AUTOREF50">{{cite news | last = Sepinwall | first = Alan | date = 2008-01-31 | url = http://blog.nj.com/alltv/2008/01/sepinwall_on_tv_lost_season_fo.html | title = ''Lost'' Season 4 Review | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140826115219/http://blog.nj.com/alltv/2008/01/sepinwall_on_tv_lost_season_fo.html | deadurl = no | newspaper = ''The Star-Ledger'' | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | archivedate = 2014-08-26}}</ref>。罗德尼·霍（{{lang|en|Rodney Ho}}）在《[[亚特兰大宪法报|亚特兰大宪法报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Atlanta Journal-Constitution''}}）上称，《结局的开始》是《迷失》“令人满意的回归，其中的戏剧性和能够打动人的部分都恰到好处……揭露的奥秘刚好能让剧迷们渴望更多”<ref name="AUTOREF51">{{cite news | last = Ho | first = Rodney | date = 2008-01-31 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120208033503/http://www.accessatlanta.com/blogs/content/shared-blogs/accessatlanta/radiotalk/entries/2008/01/31/131_lost_is_bac.html | title = ''Lost'' is Back! | newspaper = ''The Atlanta Journal-Constitution'' | url = http://www.accessatlanta.com/blogs/content/shared-blogs/accessatlanta/radiotalk/entries/2008/01/31/131_lost_is_bac.html | accessdate = 2012-02-08 | archivedate = 2012-02-08}}</ref>。《[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]]》的大卫·辛克利（{{lang|en|David Hinckley}}）给予本集的评级为3星（最高5星）<ref name="AUTOREF52">{{cite news | last = Hinckley | first = David | date = 2008-01-30 | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/lost-heading-direction-article-1.345785 | title = ''Lost'' Still Heading in the Right Direction | newspaper = ''[[纽约每日新闻|Daily News]]'' | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150124105212/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/lost-heading-direction-article-1.345785 | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | archivedate = 2015-01-24}}</ref>。

